      "content": "thanks. the massage sounds okay but i'm kinda worried about the ibuprofen dose, 3200mg seems like a lot? though if it'll actually stop this pain so i can sleep i guess it's fine. i also have some leftover oxycodone from a dental thing a while back, would it be safe to take a little bit of that with the ibuprofen so i don't wake up in pain? i'm really just trying to avoid a trip to the emergency room at this hour if i can just manage it at home.",
